  "statement": {
    "markdown": "## Accessible Dialog Chain\n### Requirements\n1. The 'Accessible Dialog Chain' consists of three buttons. When any of these buttons are clicked, it opens a corresponding dialog with a title, a description, and a close button.\n2. The dialogs must be visually hidden when they are closed, and only become visible when opened.\n3. The dialogs must use ARIA attributes for accessibility.\n4. Use Tailwind CSS classes for styling.\n5. The dialog chain must be fully keyboard navigable."
  },
  "constraints": [
    "The dialogs must be visually hidden when closed.",
    "The dialogs must use ARIA attributes for accessibility.",
    "The dialog chain must be fully keyboard navigable."
  ],
  "referenceAssets": [],
  "starterCode": {
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Accessible Dialog Chain</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center mt-10\">\n        <button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline\" aria-label=\"Button 1\" id=\"button-1\">Button 1</button>\n        <button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline\" aria-label=\"Button 2\" id=\"button-2\">Button 2</button>\n        <button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline\" aria-label=\"Button 3\" id=\"button-3\">Button 3</button>\n    </div>\n\n    <div id=\"dialog-1\" class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-50 z-10 inset-0 overflow-y-auto flex justify-center w-100 items-center justify-items-center hidden\">\n        <div class=\"inline-block align-bottom bg-white rounded-lg text-left overflow-hidden shadow-xl transform transition-all sm:my-8 sm:align-middle sm:max-w-lg sm:w-full\">\n            <div class=\"bg-white px-4 pt-5 pb-4 sm:p-6 sm:pb-4\">\n                <div class=\"sm:flex sm:items-start\">\n                    <div class=\"mt-3 text-center sm:mt-0 sm:ml-4 sm:text-left\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900\" id=\"modal-title\">\n\n                        </h3>\n                        <div class=\"mt-2\">\n                            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\" id=\"modal-description\">\n\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"mt-5 sm:mt-4 sm:ml-6 sm:flex sm:flex-row-reverse\">\n                    <button type=\"button\" class=\"bg-red-500 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline\" id=\"close-button\" aria-label=\"Close Dialog\">\n                        Close\n                    </button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div id=\"dialog-2\" class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-50 z-10 inset-0 overflow-y-auto flex justify-center w-100 items-center justify-items-center hidden\">\n        <div class=\"inline-block align-bottom bg-white rounded-lg text-left overflow-hidden shadow-xl transform transition-all sm:my-8 sm:align-middle sm:max-w-lg sm:w-full\">\n            <div class=\"bg-white px-4 pt-5 pb-4 sm:p-6 sm:pb-4\">\n                <div class=\"sm:flex sm:items-start\">\n                    <div class=\"mt-3 text-center sm:mt-0 sm:ml-4 sm:text-left\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900\" id=\"modal-title-2\">\n\n                        </h3>\n                        <div class=\"mt-2\">\n                            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\" id=\"modal-description-2\">\n\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"mt-5 sm:mt-4 sm:ml-6 sm:flex sm:flex-row-reverse\">\n                    <button type=\"button\" class=\"bg-red-500 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline\" id=\"close-button-2\" aria-label=\"Close Dialog 2\">\n                        Close\n                    </button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div id=\"dialog-3\" class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-50 z-10 inset-0 overflow-y-auto flex justify-center w-100 items-center justify-items-center hidden\">\n        <div class=\"inline-block align-bottom bg-white rounded-lg text-left overflow-hidden shadow-xl transform transition-all sm:my-8 sm:align-middle sm:max-w-lg sm:w-full\">\n            <div class=\"bg-white px-4 pt-5 pb-4 sm:p-6 sm:pb-4\">\n                <div class=\"sm:flex sm:items-start\">\n                    <div class=\"mt-3 text-center sm:mt-0 sm:ml-4 sm:text-left\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900\" id=\"modal-title-3\">\n\n                        </h3>\n                        <div class=\"mt-2\">\n                            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\" id=\"modal-description-3\">\n\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"mt-5 sm:mt-4 sm:ml-6 sm:flex sm:flex-row-reverse\">\n                    <button type=\"button\" class=\"bg-red-500 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline\" id=\"close-button-3\" aria-label=\"Close Dialog 3\">\n                        Close\n                    </button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <script src=\"script.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>",
    "css": "body {\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n}\n\n#dialog-1, #dialog-2, #dialog-3 {\n    display: none;\n}\n\n.hidden {\n    display: none;\n}",
